name: Cube Fly
description:
Welcome to Cube Fly! Try to navigate through the obstacles by flying a rocket, dashing a dasher or flipping a balloon! Try to complete the six levels with songs from artists such as Waterflame, Avenza, Boomkitty, Darude, Toby Fox and F-777!

As you might have seen already this game is NOT easy survive for roughly a minute in each frustrating level with ratings from easy to insane! Good luck.
